com.jnape.palatable.lambda.traversable

Class TraversableOptional<A>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jnape.palatable.lambda.traversable.TraversableOptional<A>
  • Type Parameters:
    A - the Optional parameter type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Functor<A,TraversableOptional>, Traversable<A,TraversableOptional>

    public final class TraversableOptional<A>
extends Object
implements Traversable<A,TraversableOptional>
    Wrap an Optional in a Traversable such that Traversable.traverse(Function, Function) applies its computation against the value wrapped by the wrapped Optional (if the Optional is present). Returns the result of pure if the wrapped Optional is empty.
